name: Dragon's Crucible Larder
text: The Dragon's Crucible Larder, successor to the famed Inferno Maw Icebox, shimmered in the alchemist's kitchen. Armed with incendiary enchantments, it safeguarded esoteric edibles with its dragon maw, which only calmed when fed by the master's hand. It stood vigilant, a fiery sentinel amongst pots and potions.
